      <title>英国加强对小船难民申请公民身份的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/uk-toughens-rules-on-small-boat-refugees-claiming-citizenship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府继续严厉打击移民，并收紧规定，防止乘坐小船抵达的难民申请公民身份。]]></description>
